<br>
<h4>Please visit our facebook page for more information <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pg/TheArtifyingFactory">The Art Factory</a></h4>
<br>
<h4>Following is the list of Packages we offer, you can filter the packages with the "Sort" option in the menu</h4>
<h1 class = "current-category"> <%= params[:category] %></h1>

<% if @packages.count ==0%>
	<h3>No Packages in this category</h3>
<%else %>
	
